overview: Sexy Amber Lynn can't keep it up - the profit margin that is - at her very exclusive travel agency, Romantic Rendezvous Inc. She enlists the x-pert help of her agents, Erik Edwards, Tracy Adams and Peter North. Since Tracy has a sweet tooth for French Bon-Bons - she gets Paris! Tracy's X-pertise will make you forget about the Champs Elysee, the Moulin Rouge and its Can-Can Girls as she takes you around the world in more ways than one. With Tracy French romance really sizzles!
title: Tracy Takes Paris
